publisher			GamesBoosters							
publish_time	 2015年9月24日		
desc_long							评测						“Missing Translation is a pixel art puzzle adventure about an abductee who must complete a series of puzzles to earn the items required to get home”7/10 – Pocket Gamer“Traditionally, adventure games are supposed to give players a clear understanding of the plot by using a clear language. But what if one of the player’s goals in such a game was also to decrypt a secret language, where only then they could really understand what was going on? This is the premise of Missing Translation, a puzzle adventure game made by the Spanish studio AlPixel Games.”Indie Game Magazine“Missing Translation plans to teach its own language that’s far simpler, a visual language based on drawing lines across a nine-node grid. That’s not the main focus of the game – it’s a puzzler at heart – but if we want to, hey, we’ll get to converse with the locals in our strange new home.”Rock Paper Shotgun												关于这款游戏							迷失在荒漠之中的古怪城市，被更加古怪的生物所包围，虎视眈眈。这是一个关于探索未知和解决谜题的游戏……超多的未知和谜题！不要被表象所欺骗，这不是你平常看到的点击解谜游戏，你需要十分努力才能揭开真相！游戏特点没有教程，没有提示，你甚至看不到文本。但是这不是为了增加游戏难度，而是要让玩家自己做主。《消失的译文》并不难，但是我们也不想让你觉得无聊！重复一遍，没有文本！不管你来自何方，讲什么语言，你都能充分享受游戏！三种不同的游戏机制，每种都有25个关卡！优雅的黑白像素风……我是不是说过了我们有养猫？两个角色可供选择。你可以在游戏中接受额外挑战，习得一种图形文字！动听的原声带也跟游戏的其它部分一样棒！免费！没有广告，没有内购，没有任何收费项！						
